        <div class="controls">
            <h3>Wybierz materia≈Ç:</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Gƒôsto≈õƒá wody to 1000 kg/m¬≥</p>

            <button class="btn-material" onclick="setMaterial('styropian')">
                ‚ö™ Styropian <span>20 kg/m¬≥</span>
            </button>
            <button class="btn-material" onclick="setMaterial('drewno')">
                ü™µ Drewno <span>700 kg/m¬≥</span>
            </button>
            <button class="btn-material" onclick="setMaterial('l√≥d')">
                üßä L√≥d <span>900 kg/m¬≥</span>
